Client Brief given: 

Create a Low Poly environment in 3DMax and publish it to Sketchfab. 

 

Disney have asked you to create a Low Poly scene as a concept for a new droid / building / location design that could be used in a new Star Wars TV Show or Movie. 

 

The environment will be in the theme of Star Wars, borrowing from one of the following planet visual styles: 

 

Tatooine 

Jedha 

Coruscant 

Hoth 

Endor 

You must add some animation (A slow spinning antenna or a droid moving around) 

